---
title: Roasted Shawarma Chicken and Squash Freekeh with Tomato Herb Salad and Lemon-Garlic Sauce
description: Fresh fruity flavours meet tender spiced chicken in this dish. Our shawarma spice blend makes a fresh, fun take on one of our favourite take-out meals.
